ible for an associate discount on JCPenney merchandise. • Job Title: Omnichannel Associate - Mall Of Georgia • J.C. Penney Company Inc', '2022-03-01 00:00:00', 'Georgia', '8.0', 'Full Time', '2022-03-01 00:00:00', 'Job Poster', 'web.com', 'company.com', 'It is a long established fact that a reader will b...', 'assets/img/icon/job-list1.png'),
