('10.0', 'Hospitalist Advanced Practice Clinician in Atlanta, Georgia', '2500usd', 'https://jooble.org/SearchResult?ukw=hospitalist+advanced+practice+clinician+in+atlanta%2c+georgia&rgns=Atlanta%2c+GA&loc=0&closedJob=True', 'TeamHealth has an excellent full-time job opportunity for a nurse practitioner or physician assistant to join our hospitalist team at University Hospital near Atlanta, Georgia. Main responsibilities in this role include rounding, admitting, and discharging. Enjoy working a flexible block schedule. The coverage model is 24x7 between day, swing and night coverage. The facility offers back-up and intensivist support. In today\'s hospital medicine environment, you\'re asked to deliver patient care with a high level of confidence. That\'s why TeamHealth puts you in the best position, with the education, training, risk management resources and support to anticipate patient needs and act on them. We are the industry leader in providing integrated hospital-based services offering the ability to grow professionally. At TeamHealth, our purpose is to perfect our clinicians\' ability to practice medicine, every day, in everything we do. Our philosophy is as simple as our goal is singular: we believe better experiences for clinicians lead to better outcomes for patients, partners, and physicians alike. For more than 40 years, TeamHealth\'s innovative national resources have supported our clinicians as they deliver the best possible patient care. Driven by our commitment to quality and safety, we are proud to be one of the largest integrated healthcare providers in the country', '2022-03-05 00:00:00', 'Georgia', '10.0', 'Full Time', '2022-03-05 00:00:00', 'Job Poster', 'web.com', 'company.com', 'It is a long established fact that a reader will b...', 'assets/img/icon/job-list1.png'),
