ccination is required as a condition of employment Benefits: • Malpractice insurance • UpToDate subscription • Flexible schedule typically consists of 1 in-clinic day every 4 weeks (can work more if requested) • Standard Drug Screen, Driving Record and Background Checks will be performed.* MAINSTREET FAMILY CARE IS AN EQUAL OPPORTUNITY EMPLOYER', '2022-03-17 00:00:00', 'Georgia', '16.0', 'Full Time', '2022-03-17 00:00:00', 'Job Poster', 'web.com', 'company.com', 'It is a long established fact that a reader will b...', 'assets/img/icon/job-list1.png'),
