('52.0', 'Job opportunity as a caddie at 18 Hole Course at Crosswinds Golf Club in...', '2500usd', 'https://bainbridge-ga.uloop.com/jobs/view.php/710190933/Job-opportunity-as-a-caddie-at-18-Hole-Course-at-Crosswinds-Golf?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'Make this a Bainbridge State College summer to remember by working as a golf caddie at 18 Hole Course at Crosswinds Golf Club in Savannah, GA. As a 18 Hole Course at Crosswinds Golf Club caddy, you will provide the highest level of professionalism and customer service for all 18 Hole Course at Crosswinds Golf Club members and guests on the course and be responsible for carrying golf bags. You will truly be an ambassador for 18 Hole Course at Crosswinds Golf Club, so being courteous, on-time and knowledgeable are all strengths that you should possess. Bainbridge State College caddies earn competitive pay and spend the majority of their time where we\'d all like to be: on the 18 Hole Course at Crosswinds Golf Club golf course. Go ahead and apply to become a golf caddie at 18 Hole Course at Crosswinds Golf Club today!', '2022-04-16 00:00:00', 'Georgia', '20.0', 'Full Time', '2022-04-16 00:00:00', 'Job Poster', 'web.com', 'company.com', 'It is a long established fact that a reader will b...', 'assets/img/icon/job-list1.png'),
('53.0', 'Scouting Assistant Internship- Georgia', '2500usd', 'https://lensa.com/scouting-assistant-internship-georgia-jobs/kennesaw/jd/9b92c47e5e5f1850df688c447fcfce81?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'Perfect Game Incorporated is seeking a Scouting Intern for our summer season! Perfect Game first opened for business over 20 years ago. Since then, Perfect Game has continued to grow and expand throughout the United States. Our mission is to promote the game of baseball now and in the future by hosting the highest quality amateur baseball events while providing meaningful opportunities and information to players, families, MLB organizations, college coaches and fans. Perfect Game is the premier provider of amateur baseball events, hosting both travel team tournaments and individual player showcases throughout the country. Our online database, scouting reports and player rankings have proven to be a valuable resource for all college coaches and MLB scouts. In addition to being recognized as the leader in high level baseball events, the PGBA, Perfect Game\'s governing baseball association, offers the opportunity for baseball organizations across the country to host PG affiliated tournaments, allowing teams across all age divisions and locations to experience Perfect Game events. The number of tournaments held each year by both Perfect Game and its\' affiliated PGBA organizations has reached well into the thousands. Whether you are a baseball enthusiast or simply want an exciting opportunity with a fast-growing company, this internship with Perfect Game may be just what you are looking for to gain valuable experience and help you further your career. RESPONSIBILITIES: • Assist Perfect Game in identifying top prospect in each graduating class at tournament and showcase events. • Able to complete the write-ups of prospects seen in a timely manner and to be posted on the website the next day. • Scouting and analyzing prospect