('54.0', 'Storm & Independent Insurance Claims Adjuster Georgia', '2500usd', 'https://www.jobilize.com/job/us-ga-eatonton-storm-independent-insurance-claims-adjuster-georgia-a36f8e4ec17fd1?utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic', 'ADJUSTERS NEEDED NOW FOR ALL STORM RELATED SEASONS!Independent Insurance Claims Adjusters Needed Now!Each year NOOA makes predictions about how the weather will be for the year. Hurricane Season is one of the most important to the adjuster industry. While some seasons are slower than others, every month is a good time to get trained because there is almost always something going on that is weather related 24/7/365. Such as Hailstorms, Tornadoes, Floods, Winter Storms, Fires, and yes, the Hurricanes! They are also predicting another cold winter coming for winter 2022!This is a HUGE opportunity for you, since there is currently a HIGH DEMAND out there for NEW ADJUSTERS AND NEW STORM ADJUSTERS!Are you actively working as a Licensed Claims Adjuster?Do you have 100 claims or more under your Belt? If you do Great! If you don\'t, No Problem! Let us help you on your career path as a Licensed Claims Adjuster.You\'re welcome to sign up on our jobs roster if you meet our guidelines.Here is how we can help.At MileHigh Adjusters Houston, our focus is assisting you in getting Trained for Success as a Licensed Claims Adjuster! Our LICENSED PROFESSIONAL INSTRUCTORS will assist in preparing you for an exciting Adjusting Career! Our expert instructors will also help prepare you for Storm Readiness including Catastrophic Events. We will show you how to go from completing one claim per day to several claims per day with ease. Our Texas All-Lines Adjuster Licensing Class, and our Deployment Boot Camp will help put you on the path towards a successful adjusting career.Come and experience our technical expertise in our Adjuster Deployment Boot Camp. Many of our Newly Trained Adjusters have attained great success while atte